    • Method Detail

      • get7BitEncoding

        public java.lang.String get7BitEncoding()
        Returns the Encoding that will be used to decode any "7 bit" (non unicode) data. Most files default to CP1252(返回将用于解码任何“7位”（非Unicode）数据的编码。大多数文件默认为CP 1252)

      • set7BitEncoding

        public void set7BitEncoding(java.lang.String encoding)
        Sets the Encoding that will be used to decode any "7 bit" (non unicode) data. This doesn't appear to be stored anywhere specific in the file, so you may need to guess by looking at headers etc(设置将用于解码任何“7位”（非unicode）数据的编码。这似乎没有存储在文件中特定的任何地方，因此您可能需要通过查看标题等来猜测)
